{"tid":1266997,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「假消息」到處流傳，PTT 被指是幫兇","createTime":"2019-06-29T16:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T09:44:12.000Z","uid":47905,"like":81,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"eb5ae0e7c0ae96742e70c7611f74eac4f6272864","tid":1266997,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:52:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://buzzorange.com/techorange/2018/09/17/ptt-stop-accept-new-account/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2Ftechorange%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2Fptt-stop-accept-new-account%2F&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJozWqReVd2N9LFFOFvvIGphw%3D&h=f52bfb54\" target=\"_blank\">https://buzzorange.com/techorange/2018/09/17/ptt-stop-accept-new-account/</a><br />\n<br />\n9 月 15 日，PTT 批踢踢實業坊發布了重大的決策消息：暫時停止新帳號註冊。<br />\n<br />\n在過去的時間中，PTT 很少做出這樣的決定，之所以這次會出現這樣的決策，大眾推估應該與兩件事前有關，那就是不久前發生的台灣駐大阪辦事處處長輕生事件，以及年底 9 合 1 大選的緣故。<br />\n<br />\n這兩件事情的共同點在於，大阪辦事處事件中當事人之所以<span style=\"color: red;\">輕生</span>，起因於網路上流傳著「中國在日本天災後派專車接人出機場」的<span style=\"color: red;\">假消息</span>，而往年選舉中，都會有許多人在網路上任意散布假消息、<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">用錯誤的資訊引導民意</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「假消息」到處流傳，PTT 被指是幫兇</span><br />\n<br />\n連尼住,你明唔明3毛放假POST,放負能量<br />\n係可以帶起民意,令到好多人都多負能量同想效法架?<br />\n<br />\n仲唔禁止註冊 再有香港人跳樓自殺<br />\n你都係幫兇之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1266050/page/29\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1266050/page/29</a><br />\n依家非常時期你可以免廣告<br />\n但停註冊都做唔到?<br />\n我寧願睇廣告都唔想3毛帶風向,唔想香港人再自殺呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad11c467927c40bb5c4f4fd2fe9ad18e87816774","tid":1266997,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:54:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連尼住"},{"pid":"9ef17cf59752a74f74324f4f77818c72daa5a61b","tid":1266997,"uid":76163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:55:59.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"fed88836afdd905bec37756bb4d7d63bcd31fbbd","tid":1266997,"uid":158646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:57:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"94fd4524744e72027dc2c22402fc2713476cdb97","tid":1266997,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:58:42.000Z","msg":"人手推POST"},{"pid":"f3de3d637aa5a1864e196547c82d58b52eff76be","tid":1266997,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77de8e9981e05fef5a65b58be000b2bde771ca95","tid":1266997,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ae05094341a5f773d9bdb393fcb517d031ca77","tid":1266997,"uid":8316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:59:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd469555054328962f3441ff9a1f34cfb3a84035","tid":1266997,"uid":259675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:59:27.000Z","msg":"pish!!"},{"pid":"62ba4cc67416cb2482c7ca8835300328aa1aa017","tid":1266997,"uid":267395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:00:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e97ec1e67a50a9b20463bb974353829b655b33b","tid":1266997,"uid":151702,"like":0,"disli